excerpt: Built entirely with hand-hewn wood carvings, this still unfinished 20-story complex offers tours.

excerpt: Horseback riding for kids, rodeo shows & a reptile gallery, plus feeding & petting Shetland ponies.
detail_description: Nestled in the enchanting East Pattaya, Pipo Pony Club is a delightful destination for families seeking fun and adventure. This unique miniature horse farm is Thailand's first of its kind, featuring adorable Shetland ponies that kids can feed and ride. The whimsical atmosphere includes pony-themed toys and props inspired by beloved characters from Little Pony, perfect for capturing memorable photos.
